== 反響 ==
《史前巨鱷》獲得的評價褒貶不一。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度39%<ref name=RottenTom>{{cite web |title=Lake Placid (1999) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lake_placid/ |accessdate=2015-09-06 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925160331/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lake_placid |dead-url=no }}</ref>。知名影評人[[羅傑·伊伯特|羅傑·伊伯特]]將其形容為「從頭完全錯誤到尾」<ref name=Ebert>{{cite news |last=Ebert |first=Roger |title=Lake Placid |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/19990716/REVIEWS/907160303/1023 |date=July 16, 1999 |newspaper=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]] |via=RogerEbert.com |accessdate=2015-09-06 |archive-date=2012-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120926133706/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F19990716%2FREVIEWS%2F907160303%2F1023 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。相反地，《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》給了電影四星的好評（滿分五星），認為《史前巨鱷》是一部娛樂性足夠的簡單電影<ref name=Empire>{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/review.asp?FID=5616 |title=Lake Placid |website=Empire |accessdate=2015-09-06 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924133043/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/review.asp?FID=5616 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《史前巨鱷》在全球獲得5687萬美元的票房，對比2700萬美元的成本可謂成功。

